strings: <voice_0x0100139C><se_high>Dye: Why is it taking so long? Doesn't that sound like a present? Say "first come, first served"!
<voice_0x0100139D><se_low>Chief Raven: My name is Captain Crewe. I was once a pirate who traveled the seven seas...
<voice_0x0100139E><se_low>Chief Raven: Do you think you can accept my baby? Think you a genius?
<voice_0x010013A0><se_low>Chief Raven: Or you'll take back my jewellery!
<voice_0x010013A2><se_low>January: Red How did you get to this place? That's the problem
